hm2L2McastMib.name: hm2L2McastMib

hm2L2McastSnoopingQuerierTable.name: hm2L2McastSnoopingQuerierTable
hm2L2McastSnoopingQuerierTable.description: A table for displaying and configuring the IGMP query ports.

hm2L2McastSnoopingQuerierEntry.name: hm2L2McastSnoopingQuerierEntry
hm2L2McastSnoopingQuerierEntry.description: A table for displaying and configuring the IGMP query ports. An entry appears in this table for all VLANs that are currently instantiated.

hm2L2McastSnoopingQueryPorts.name: hm2L2McastSnoopingQueryPorts
hm2L2McastSnoopingQueryPorts.description: This read-only object displays the set of ports that have received IGMP query PDUs for this VLAN as determined by the snooping task.

hm2L2McastSnoopingQueryStaticPorts.name: hm2L2McastSnoopingQueryStaticPorts
hm2L2McastSnoopingQueryStaticPorts.description: The set of ports explicitly configured by management to be IGMP query ports for this VLAN.

hm2L2McastSnoopingQueryPortsAutoPorts.name: hm2L2McastSnoopingQueryPortsAutoPorts
hm2L2McastSnoopingQueryPortsAutoPorts.description: The set of ports that are automatically learned by LLDP protocol to be IGMP query ports for this VLAN.

hm2L2McastSnoopingQueryPortsAutoPortsSta.name: hm2L2McastSnoopingQueryPortsAutoPortsState
hm2L2McastSnoopingQueryPortsAutoPortsSta.description: The set of ports that are allowed to be learned automatically by LLDP protocol to be IGMP query ports for this VLAN.

hm2L2McastSnoopingForwardAllTable.name: hm2L2McastSnoopingForwardAllTable
hm2L2McastSnoopingForwardAllTable.description: A table containing forwarding information for each VLAN, specifying the set of ports to which forwarding of all multicasts applies, which are dynamically learnt.

hm2L2McastSnoopingForwardAllEntry.name: hm2L2McastSnoopingForwardAllEntry
hm2L2McastSnoopingForwardAllEntry.description: Forwarding information for a VLAN, specifying the set of ports to which all multicasts should be forwarded, which are dynamically learnt. An entry appears in this table for all VLANs that are currently instantiated.

hm2L2McastSnoopingForwardAllStaticPorts.name: hm2L2McastSnoopingForwardAllStaticPorts
hm2L2McastSnoopingForwardAllStaticPorts.description: The set of ports configured by management in this VLAN to which all dyamically learnt multicast group-addressed frames are to be forwarded.

hm2L2McastFilteringTable.name: hm2L2McastFilteringTable
hm2L2McastFilteringTable.description: A table for configuring the filtering behaviour for known multicast group-addressed frames.

hm2L2McastFilteringEntry.name: hm2L2McastFilteringEntry
hm2L2McastFilteringEntry.description: A table for configuring the filtering behaviour for known multicast group-addressed frames. An entry appears in this table for all VLANs that are currently instantiated.

hm2L2McastFilteringKnownMode.name: hm2L2McastFilteringKnownMode
hm2L2McastFilteringKnownMode.description: Sets the mode how known multicast packets will be treated. The default value is registered-ports-only(2).

hm2L2McastFilteringUnknownMode.name: hm2L2McastFilteringUnknownMode
hm2L2McastFilteringUnknownMode.description: Sets the mode how unknown multicast packets will be treated. The default value is flood(2).

hm2L2McastSnoopingIgmpReportsFramesProce.name: hm2L2McastSnoopingIgmpReportsFramesProcessed
hm2L2McastSnoopingIgmpReportsFramesProce.description: IGMP reports, joins or leaves processed by CPU. The number of multicast control frames that have been processed by the CPU.

hm2L2McastSnoopingIgmpQueriesV1FramesPro.name: hm2L2McastSnoopingIgmpQueriesV1FramesProcessed
hm2L2McastSnoopingIgmpQueriesV1FramesPro.description: IGMP queries version 1 processed by CPU. The number of multicast control frames that have been processed by the CPU.

hm2L2McastSnoopingIgmpQueriesV2FramesPro.name: hm2L2McastSnoopingIgmpQueriesV2FramesProcessed
hm2L2McastSnoopingIgmpQueriesV2FramesPro.description: IGMP queries version 2 processed by CPU. The number of multicast control frames that have been processed by the CPU.

hm2L2McastSnoopingIgmpQueriesV3FramesPro.name: hm2L2McastSnoopingIgmpQueriesV3FramesProcessed
hm2L2McastSnoopingIgmpQueriesV3FramesPro.description: IGMP queries version 3 processed by CPU. The number of multicast control frames that have been processed by the CPU.

hm2L2McastSnoopingIgmpWrongVersionQuerie.name: hm2L2McastSnoopingIgmpWrongVersionQueries
hm2L2McastSnoopingIgmpWrongVersionQuerie.description: The number of general queries received whose IGMP version does not match the equivalent hm2AgentSwitchSnoopingQuerierVersion.

hm2L2McastSnoopingPimDvmrpFramesProcesse.name: hm2L2McastSnoopingPimDvmrpFramesProcessed
hm2L2McastSnoopingPimDvmrpFramesProcesse.description: PIM or DVMRP frames processed by CPU. The number of multicast control frames that have been processed by the CPU.

hm2L2McastSnoopingStatisticsTable.name: hm2L2McastSnoopingStatisticsTable
hm2L2McastSnoopingStatisticsTable.description: A table for multicast control frames that have been processed by the CPU.

hm2L2McastSnoopingStatisticsEntry.name: hm2L2McastSnoopingStatisticsEntry
hm2L2McastSnoopingStatisticsEntry.description: A table for multicast control frames that have been processed by the CPU. An entry appears in this table for any physical interfaces.

hm2L2McastSnoopingIntfIgmpReportsFramesP.name: hm2L2McastSnoopingIntfIgmpReportsFramesProcessed
hm2L2McastSnoopingIntfIgmpReportsFramesP.description: IGMP reports, joins or leaves processed by CPU and received on the interface. The number of multicast control frames that have been processed by the CPU.

hm2L2McastSnoopingIntfIgmpQueriesV1Frame.name: hm2L2McastSnoopingIntfIgmpQueriesV1FramesProcessed
hm2L2McastSnoopingIntfIgmpQueriesV1Frame.description: IGMP queries version 1 processed by CPU and received on the interface. The number of multicast control frames that have been processed by the CPU.

hm2L2McastSnoopingIntfIgmpQueriesV2Frame.name: hm2L2McastSnoopingIntfIgmpQueriesV2FramesProcessed
hm2L2McastSnoopingIntfIgmpQueriesV2Frame.description: IGMP queries version 2 processed by CPU and received on the interface. The number of multicast control frames that have been processed by the CPU.

hm2L2McastSnoopingIntfIgmpQueriesV3Frame.name: hm2L2McastSnoopingIntfIgmpQueriesV3FramesProcessed
hm2L2McastSnoopingIntfIgmpQueriesV3Frame.description: IGMP queries version 3 processed by CPU and received on the interface. The number of multicast control frames that have been processed by the CPU.

hm2L2McastSnoopingIntfIgmpWrongVersionQu.name: hm2L2McastSnoopingIntfIgmpWrongVersionQueries
hm2L2McastSnoopingIntfIgmpWrongVersionQu.description: The number of general queries received whose IGMP version does not match the equivalent hm2AgentSwitchSnoopingQuerierVersion.

hm2L2McastSnoopingIntfPimDvmrpFramesProc.name: hm2L2McastSnoopingIntfPimDvmrpFramesProcessed
hm2L2McastSnoopingIntfPimDvmrpFramesProc.description: PIM or DVMRP frames processed by CPU and received on the interface. The number of multicast control frames that have been processed by the CPU.

hm2L2McastGroupMembershipErrorReturn.name: hm2L2McastGroupMembershipErrorReturn
hm2L2McastGroupMembershipErrorReturn.description: Indicates that Max Response Time is greater than the Group Membership Interval
